headline: Terreno Realty (TRNO) Q4 FFO Match Estimates
summary: Terreno (TRNO) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of 0% and 2.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: American Tower Corporation Announces Election of Rajesh Kalathur to Board of Directors
summary: BOSTON, February 05, 2025--American Tower Corporation (NYSE: AMT) announced that its Board of Directors (the "Board") has elected Rajesh ("Raj") Kalathur as a director.
